name: CatData
0:
”Alexa, tell Cat Data that I gave the cat her medicine”
”Alexa, ask Cat Data did anyone feed the cat”
”Alexa, tell Cat data that I emptied the litter box”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat data
des: Cat Data helps to keep track of when your cat has been fed, let out or given medication. This can be especially helpful when multiple people feed your cat, or with long term medications that you only need to give your cat once a week or once a month. Cat Data can also remember when you emptied the litter box or changed the kitty litter.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
